#. Tag: title
#: firsttime.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a new file"
msgstr "Criar um novo ficheiro"

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; keeps all the data about your finances in a file. As was stated "
"in <link linkend=\"makingmostof.basicaccounting.personalaccounts\">Defining "
"the accounts (personal records)</link>, you can keep more than one set of "
"accounts, but the data for each will be kept in a separate file, and "
"&kmymoney; can only have one file open at a time. See the chapter on <link "
"linkend=\"details.formats\">File Formats</link> for more details about "
"&kmymoney;'s data files."
msgstr ""
"O &kmymoney; mantém todos os dados acerca das suas finanças num ficheiro. "
"Como foi definido em <link linkend=\"makingmostof.basicaccounting."
"personalaccounts\">Definir as contas (registos pessoais)</link>, poderá "
"manter mais de um conjunto de contas, mas os dados de cada um será guardado "
"num ficheiro separado, sendo que o &kmymoney; só pode ter um ficheiro aberto "
"de cada vez. Veja o capítulo sobre <link linkend=\"details.formats"
"\">Formatos de Ficheiros</link> para obter mais detalhes sobre os ficheiros "
"de dados do &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to that data file with all the financial data for that set of "
"accounts, &kmymoney; uses additional files to store data regarding "
"configuration settings and display preferences. The exact location of these "
"files depends on your specific Operating System or Distribution."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: firsttime.docbook:309
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To create a new file you can either select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or choose "
#| "the <guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"new.png"
#| "\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> new icon "
#| "from the toolbar. In addition, if the main welcome page is displayed, you "
#| "can also select the first link: \"Get started and setup accounts.\""
msgid ""
"To create a new file you can either select the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
